    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic restoration. The engine currently has trouble starting, and there are noticeable leaks that need to be addressed immediately. The body shows substantial wear, including rust spots and several dents, while the interior requires a deep clean and repair of torn upholstery. This is a project car best suited for someone with the tools and expertise to perform a full overhaul.",
