    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior is flawless, with original paint that shines perfectly and no imperfections whatsoever. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is in peak performance, with every system functioning like new and a complete service history to document its meticulous care.",
