    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for! We are thrilled to offer this absolute gem, which is in truly mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously maintained, offering a pristine driving experience that is rare to find. If you're looking for perfection and a car that feels brand new, this stunning vehicle is ready for its next proud owner!",
      "price": 48500.0,
